                                <fo:block-container space-after="0.5em" margin-left="0" margin-right="0" space-before="0.5em"><fo:block end-indent="0" start-indent="0">You can download this manual also as a <fo:inline color="rgb(97 , 168 , 223)"><fo:basic-link show-destination="new" indicate-destination="true" external-destination="docs/how_to_choose_tms.pdf">pdf
